== 評價 ==
=== 票房 ===
《黑天鵝》於2010年12月3日在[[北美|北美]]的一些選定城市中的18個影院中有一個限定上映<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/swan-breaks-studio-record-prestige-56492|title='Black Swan' Breaks Studio Record as Prestige Films Make Impressive Debuts, Expansions|date=2010-12-05|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|last=DiOrio|first=Carl|accessdate=2012-08-11|archive-date=2011-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111227032251/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/swan-breaks-studio-record-prestige-56492|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且得到一個驚喜的票房成功<ref>{{cite news | url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jan/16/entertainment/la-et-0116-black-swan-20110116 | work=Los Angeles Times | title='Black Swan's' risks pay off | date=2011-01-16 | accessdate=2012-05-07 | first1=Steven | last1=Zeitchik | first2=Ben | last2=Fritz | archive-date=2014-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614114839/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jan/16/entertainment/la-et-0116-black-swan-20110116 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於開幕當日已總共賺得$415,822美元，平均每得影院賺得$23,101美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=blackswan.htm |title=Daily Box Office for Friday, December 3, 2010 |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb |date=2010-12-06 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |archive-date=2010-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101208150117/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=blackswan.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在開幕周末結束時賺得$1,443,809美元，平均每得影院賺得$80,212美元，平均每個地點收益是2010年的最高開畫周末的第二位，僅次於《[[皇上無話兒|皇上無話兒]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/12/05/box-office-report-tangled/ |title=Box office report: ''Tangled'' wins slow weekend with $21.5 mil |last=Young |first=John |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2010-12-05 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |archive-date=2010-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101208030550/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/12/05/box-office-report-tangled/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>電影是[[福斯探照燈|福斯探照燈]]每影院有史以來平均最高收益，它在全天候電影列表中排行第21<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3004&p=.htm |title=Arthouse Audit: Black Swan Soars |last=Subers |first=Ray |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2010-12-06 |accessdate=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2010-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101207021630/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3004&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在上映的第二個周末它擴展到90個影院，票房收益達$3,300,00美元，成為票房的第6位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3009&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: ''Narnia'' Fails to Tread Water, ''Tourist'' Trips |last=Gray |first=Brandon |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2010-12-13 |accessdate=2010-12-19 |archive-date=2010-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101216151928/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3009&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在第三個周末，電影再擴展到959家影院上映，賺得$8,383,479美元。電影於美國共賺得$106,000,000美元，全球共賺得$329,000,000美元<ref name="mojo">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=blackswan.htm |title=Black Swan (2010) |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2011-09-10 |archive-date=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229145616/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=blackswan.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 反應評價 ===
[[File:Black_Swan_press_2010.jpg|alt=Scott Franklin, Mila Kunis, Vincent Cassel, Darren Aronofsky, and a moderator stand on a stage with a golden curtain backdrop wearing formal attire and discussing Black Swan]]
《黑天鵝》得到了廣泛的好評，在評論網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站上，從297則評論中，得到85%的評價，平均得分為8.2/10。<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_swan_2010/ |title=Black Swan Movie reviews, Pictures |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2010-12-11 |archive-date=2013-02-18 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_swan_2010/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據網站，對電影被一致評為「令人振奮的熱情，充滿激情，和狂放地濫情的元素，黑天鵝依照導演大膽的方向演變 — 以及[[娜塔莉·波曼|妮妲莉寶雯]]大膽嘗試的演出<ref name="RT"/>。」在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上，從100個主流評論中，該片獲得79%的得分，當中的42個評為「整體看好」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/black-swan |title=Black Swan |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2012-09-18 |archive-date=2012-04-14 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66v9lMeFV?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/black-swan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年9月，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》報導，根據[[威尼斯電影節|威尼斯電影節]]的電影放映評論，《黑天鵝》成為了該年度的「最愛/最恨電影<ref>{{cite news |last=Markovitz |first=Adam |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/09/02/black-swan/ |title=Is Darren Aronofsky's ''Black Swan'' a masterpiece? Early buzz from the Venice Film Festival |date=2010-09-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRp5nJdF?url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/09/02/black-swan/ |archivedate=2010-09-02 |access-date=2010-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 」。影評人{{tsl|en|Leonard Maltin|Leonard Maltin}}在他的網誌《瘋狂電影》中，承認對這齣電影不能抗拒，並讚賞[[娜塔莉·波曼|妮妲莉寶雯]]的演出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/leonardmaltin/archives/film_review_black_swan/ |title=film review: BLACK SWAN |author=Leonard Maltin |publisher=Blogs.indiewire.com |date= |accessdate=2012-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318223813/http://blogs.indiewire.com/leonardmaltin/archives/film_review_black_swan |archive-date=2011-03-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[路透社|路透社]]描述電影早期的反應是「大部分正面」，而[[娜塔莉·波曼|妮妲莉寶雯]]的表現獲得高度讚譽<ref>{{cite news |last=Collett-White |first=Mike |url=http://abcnews.go.com/print?id=11543983 |title=Natalie Portman Earns Early Awards Buzz for Ballet Drama |publisher=ABC |location=USA |agency=Reuters |date=2010-09-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sS8cunbN?url=http://abcnews.go.com/print?id=11543983 |archivedate=2010-09-02 |access-date=2010-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]]》的報導指電影收到批評，一些稱其戲劇性讓人發狂，但大部分說自己對電影的內容「一掃而空<ref>{{cite news |last=Bunbury |first=Stephanie |url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/venices-red-carpet-fades-but-movie-magic-shines-bright-20100904-14vds.html |title=Venice's red carpet fades but movie magic shines bright |work=Sydney Morning Herald |date=2010-09-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sUuIEdIc?url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/venices-red-carpet-fades-but-movie-magic-shines-bright-20100904-14vds.html |archivedate=2010-09-04 |access-date=2010-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」。

