'''黑天鵝：電影原聲帶'''（'''''Black Swan: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack'''''）是非原創音樂，音樂由[[柴可夫斯基|柴可夫斯基]]作曲，以及一首電子舞曲由英國製作二人組合[[化學兄弟|化學兄弟]]製作。那是導演艾洛諾夫斯基和作曲家[[克林特·曼塞爾|克林特·曼塞爾]]第5次連續合作，他為電影創作原創音樂。

曼塞爾原先試圖改編[[柴可夫斯基|柴可夫斯基]]的芭蕾原曲來製作配樂<ref name="Tchaikovsky">{{cite web |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Interview-Darren-Aronofsky-On-Music-Scares-And-Gender-In-Black-Swan-21985.html |title=Interview: Darren Aronofsky On Music, Scares And Gender In Black Swan |last=Rich |first=Katey |publisher=''[[Cinema_Blend|Cinema Blend]]'' |date=2010-12-02 |accessdate=2010-12-12 |archive-date=2010-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101208222243/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Interview-Darren-Aronofsky-On-Music-Scares-And-Gender-In-Black-Swan-21985.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，不過最後在音樂上作了徹底的變動<ref name="Score">{{cite web |url=http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/interviews/clint-mansell-8937 |title=Clint Mansell interview |publisher=''[[Independent_Film_Channel|Independent Film Channel]]'' |last=Wright |first=James |date=2009-12-17 |accessdate=2010-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101130200313/http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/interviews/clint-mansell-8937 |archive-date=2010-11-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。因為使用柴可夫斯基的音樂，曼塞爾所作的電影配樂因此失去入圍[[第83屆奧斯卡金像獎|第83屆]][[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡]][[奧斯卡最佳原創配樂獎|最佳原創配樂]]的提名資格<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118029326 |title=Academy nixes four score contenders |work=Variety |date=2010-12-21 |accessdate=2010-12-24 |first=Jon |last=Burlingame |archive-date=2010-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224062122/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118029326/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至於英國二人組合[[化學兄弟|化學兄弟]]製作的多種新曲風，他們的音樂在《黑天鵝》電影中的俱樂部場景中出現，不過他們的曲目沒有收錄在官方原聲帶當中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.britishmusicguide.com/2010/12/08/chemical-brothers-pen-new-tracks-for-black-swan |title=Chemical Brothers pen new songs for "Black Swan" |publisher=''British Music Guide'' |accessdate=2010-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113063942/http://www.britishmusicguide.com/2010/12/08/chemical-brothers-pen-new-tracks-for-black-swan |archive-date=2014-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
